1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:07,000
Rook secures construction milestone payments.

2
00:00:07,000 --> 00:00:17,000
In a renovation project, the client wants protection against paying too early, while the artisan needs reliable payment once the work is accepted.

3
00:00:17,000 --> 00:00:29,000
Kitchen renovation, Phase 1: 3,000 USDC total, 2,850 USDC released today, and 150 USDC protected as retention.

4
00:00:29,000 --> 00:00:42,000
Rook checks the evidence: client acceptance, invoice, compliance, no dispute, and completion photos.

5
00:00:42,000 --> 00:00:53,000
Then a deterministic payment policy decides whether the release is safe to execute.

6
00:00:53,000 --> 00:01:09,000
The approved release has already been executed through KeeperHub on Sepolia with simulation, broadcast, and an authoritative audit trail.

7
00:01:09,000 --> 00:01:22,000
The live proof shows the execution ID, transaction hash, gas used, timestamp, audit status, and explorer link.

8
00:01:22,000 --> 00:01:35,000
When client acceptance is missing, Rook safely blocks the payment before execution.

9
00:01:35,000 --> 00:01:46,000
Rook pays when evidence is complete, protects retention, and records every KeeperHub execution.

10
00:01:46,000 --> 00:01:55,000
Rook. Secure milestone payments for construction. Executed through KeeperHub.
